column5: Great pictures, always nice to see.
Looks like he had a good time, which is always good to see.
Thanks guys, He loved icefishing and wants to go again NOW...lol  I love watching him grow and look forward to more good times with my fishing buddy!
Those pictures are excellent, thanks for putting them up !!!!  It's always great to see kids learning new things and doing them for the 1st time
Great great pictures!  The smile on his face says it all, and makes it all worth it.
Vanselena you wouldn't of happened to be  5 or 6 miles East of London in those picks were ya?
Yup, a very good friend of mine owns the place
I've known Murry since I was 5 or 6.Great guy. I live about 1.5 miles away.
Hmmm do you know a guy named Matthew that was from Toronto and fished Simcoe alot?
